### Stateline, Nevada

This is about the census-designated place in [Douglas County](/Douglas_County,_Nevada), [Nevada](/Nevada). Don’t confuse it with some other place that just sounds similar. It's not [State Line, Nevada](/Primm,_Nevada), which is a whole different kind of desolate.

